longBusinessSummary: Netcoins Holdings Inc. does not have significant operations. The Company will be focused on investing in various industries, including life sciences, mining and exploration, industrial, and technology industries. Previously, it was engaged in the development and marketing of a software to make consumers purchase and sale of cryptocurrency through brokerage services. The company is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
